                div(class = "section_content") 

                  p.
                    Hobbies are a great way to let yourself have some time to be creative or just to relax. I have many hobbies I 
                    enjoy but never enough time to actually do them all. Some of my favorite hobbies are painting, reading mystery 
                    or thriller books, watching Netflix, Hulu, and Paramount series or movies, coloring in adult coloring books, 
                    making polymer clay sculptures and making graphic design elements and images on my computer. I have several different 
                    kinds of software programs I use for my graphic designing which include Photoshop, Paint Shop Pro Ultimate 6X and 2X, 
                    Gimp, Inkscape, Magix Xara Graphic Designer, Clip Studio Paint Pro, SmoothDraw and DrawPlus X4. As you can tell 
                    I have numerous programs I use when designing and they all have different features which gives me alot to choose
                    from! 
                  p.
                    Those are just the inside hobbies lol! Some of my favorite outside hobbies consist of photography, practicing shooting
                    my handguns and bow, working on cars, weedeaters, lawnmowers, planting flowers and feeding the hummingbirds! My cats love
